{"tid":2121484,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：DayDayCook朱嘉盈拍板參選","createTime":"2020-07-23T10:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T04:59:31.000Z","uid":78546,"like":9,"dislike":228,"uniUserReply":79,"replies":[{"pid":"72d3adc2c3372a354f5fdaeacc026056f1905c3d","tid":2121484,"uid":78546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:34:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200723/s00002/1595443068718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200723%2Fs00002%2F1595443068718&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=deb691ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200723%2Fs00002%2F1595443068718&h=67cd915c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200723/s00002/1595443068718</a><br />\n<br />\nEmily早前聽聞DayDayCook創辦人朱嘉盈（Norma Chu）會參選立法會資訊科技界，亦聽聞佢「有包袱」未放低，所以未明言參選。噚日Emily接獲可靠消息話Norma終於拍板去馬。<br />\n<br />\nEmily聽聞Norma會代表建制派出選，同接替莫乃光嘅IT界選委黃浩華拗手瓜。消息人士話，建制陣營計過數，1.3萬嘅IT界選民中，估計民主派有約6000張本來會投莫乃光嘅票，但估計黃浩華未必能吸盡，打個折會拎到5000票左右；又估計建制陣營約有4000張鐵票，此消彼長下，即有約4000張「游離票」，認為由建制色彩較少嘅Norma出選「樂觀一啲」，形容「有得打」。消息人士認為黃浩華知名度唔高，但亦擔心Norma太遲宣布參選會拖慢佢嘅選舉工程，所以已經有人「催下佢」。據悉，Norma會喺短期內見記者。"},{"pid":"05485e7cb3ab2c10d31f97dfec9c674d3ae8154a","tid":2121484,"uid":12599,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"打飛機就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"984f91d9f939a1aa4d26a277a2d00047a437272f","tid":2121484,"uid":21545,"like":79,"dislike":3,"score":76,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T10:36:47.000Z","msg":"Day day drop 條女識撚IT<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clo